{"lemma":"جَحْشاتٌ","slug":"جَحْشاتٌ","root":"ج.ح.ش","root_slug":"ج-ح-ش","root_link":"/words/roots/ج-ح-ش","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n5116"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AC%D9%8E%D8%AD%D9%92%D8%B4%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"young donkey"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"trestle, horse"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n5116","headword_ar":"جَحْشٌ","root":"jH$","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A young ass;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"domestic"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wild:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"before it becomes big:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from the time when it is brought forth until it becomes big from sucking:"},{"kind":"text","text":"when it has completed the year, it is called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tawolabN","text_ar":"تَوْلَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (As:) [or the latter is applied to a wild ass of that age:] pl. [of pauc.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajoHaA$N","text_ar":"اَجْحَاشٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(so in a copy of the S) and [of mult.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jiHaA$N","text_ar":"جِحَاشٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jiHo$aAnN","text_ar":"جِحْشَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"juHuw$N","text_ar":"جُحُوشٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jiHa$apN","text_ar":"جِحَشَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (As, TA:) [dim."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"juHayo$N","text_ar":"جُحَيْشٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":] and fem."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaHo$apN","text_ar":"جَحْشَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, K.) It is said in a prov.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AljaHo$a lam~aA ba*~aka AlA^aEoyaAru","text_ar":"الجَحْشَ لَمَّا بَذَّكَ الاَعْيَارُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A, TA,) i. e., Seek thou, or pursue thou,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the young ass when the full-grown asses outstrip thee:"},{"kind":"text","text":"applied to him who seeks much, and it escapes him; so one says to him, Seek thou less than that. (TA.) [Meyd gives"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faAtaka","text_ar":"فَاتَكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the place of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ba*~aka","text_ar":"بَذَّكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b2-  Also (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A mare's colt;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, K;) as being likened to a young ass. (TA.) ―         -b3-  And (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A gazelle;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ibn- 'Abbád, K;) in the dial. of Hudheyl: (TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a young gazelle;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA;) in that dial.; occurring in a poem of Aboo-Dhu-eyb; but accord. to one relation, the word there is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"x$of","text_ar":"خشْف"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["TA","As","S","Msb","K","A"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}